The '''Bay of Tears''' was a deep water harbor on [[Vjun/Legends|Vjun]] guarded by sudden shoals. The shores of the bay had a network of caves and tunnels that had been carved by the [[River Weeping]]. Some of these caves exited into the cellars of [[Château Malreaux]]. The Bay was considered the perfect [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler's]] port and was used by the [[first Count Malreaux]] to launch [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] raids against the nobles in the surrounding territory. <ref name="YDR" />

